1088
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:35,560
 I ja sam došao i spričao sam se tom.

1089
00:39:35,560 --> 00:39:39,560
 Ne znam, ali bilo ovaj mladić.

1090
00:39:39,560 --> 00:39:41,560
 I on to čuo.

1091
00:39:41,560 --> 00:39:42,560
 Moji prijatelji brako.

1092
00:39:42,560 --> 00:39:43,560
 Postalo mene i kaže:

1093
00:39:43,560 --> 00:39:44,560
 "Ikend."

1094
00:39:44,560 --> 00:39:47,560
 "Dok kvoldeji se nikada nikada nispreča."

1095
00:39:47,560 --> 00:39:48,560
 Meno ga upatilo.

1096
00:39:48,560 --> 00:39:51,560
 Znaš kako sam ja papak kvoldeji se nisprečao.

1097
00:39:51,560 --> 00:39:53,560
 I ja se isprištao.

1098
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,560
 Nekako ulazi.

1099
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,560
 Jer ne znaš nam kako bi se postao.

1100
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:58,560
 Misliš da dobro treba biti u tvojim princi,

1101
00:39:58,560 --> 00:39:59,560
 da ti nisi mlad,

1102
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:00,560
 da ti nisi neki meku ušaj,

1103
00:40:00,560 --> 00:40:02,560
 da ti moraš biti u stamenu,

1104
00:40:02,560 --> 00:40:04,560
 da tebi ne trebala milost,

1105
00:40:04,560 --> 00:40:06,560
 da tebi samo nekako trebalići što treba rati.

1106
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,560
 Dakle, zapravo prevara.

1107
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:09,560
 Prevara.

1108
00:40:09,560 --> 00:40:10,560
 Ti si biti u milosti,

1109
00:40:10,560 --> 00:40:12,560
 ti si malo krko,

1110
00:40:12,560 --> 00:40:14,560
 nestabilno, nestalno,

1111
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:16,560
 nemoćno stvorenje.

1112
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:18,560
 A postoji netko

1113
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:20,560
 ko te šamara, kad god god će,

1114
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,560
 i gdje god stigne.

1115
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:24,560
 I kad idješ u razreći,

1116
00:40:24,560 --> 00:40:26,560
 jer to se naš krcerovi,

1117
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:30,560
 obitelji su uvijek imale ovako,

1118
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:32,560
 većinom puno djece,

1119
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,560
 i onda djeta su se morala

1120
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:36,560
 malo probijati kroz svijet,

1121
00:40:36,560 --> 00:40:38,560
 a mi smo bili polo agresivna sredina,

1122
00:40:38,560 --> 00:40:40,560
 i uvijek je bila nekakvi tuča u razredu,

1123
00:40:40,560 --> 00:40:42,560
 i kad je neko jačiji od tebe,

1124
00:40:42,560 --> 00:40:44,560
 onda to on malo mlati,

1125
00:40:44,560 --> 00:40:46,560
 jer uvijek ima neko koji je jačiji.

1126
00:40:46,560 --> 00:40:48,560
 A od ovek je bilo zanimljivo,

1127
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:50,560
 a to bi znali starija braća,

1128
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:52,560
 i strijučevi, i ne znam ne,

1129
00:40:52,560 --> 00:40:53,560
 kubovi,

1130
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:54,560
 onda bi rekli,

1131
00:40:54,560 --> 00:40:55,560
 nemoj da ti to vlati,

1132
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:56,560
 ako ti to bude dirao,

1133
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:57,560
 reći ne,

1134
00:40:57,560 --> 00:40:59,560
 jer ti imaš nekoga,

1135
00:40:59,560 --> 00:41:00,560
 ako me ćeš reći,

1136
00:41:00,560 --> 00:41:02,560
 ti si više problem.

1137
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:09,560
 zapravo, isto je i sada,

1138
00:41:09,560 --> 00:41:10,560
 isto je i sada.

1139
00:41:10,560 --> 00:41:12,560
 Ja idem u razredu,

1140
00:41:12,560 --> 00:41:13,560
 idem u školu,

1141
00:41:13,560 --> 00:41:14,560
 idem u život,

1142
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:16,560
 i uvijek ima netko ko me može tlačiti,

1143
00:41:16,560 --> 00:41:18,560
 koliko kod hoće.

1144
00:41:18,560 --> 00:41:22,560
 Nema tako jako frajera,

1145
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:23,560
 ni branitelja,

1146
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:24,560
 ni doboljuba,

1147
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:25,560
 ni popa,

1148
00:41:25,560 --> 00:41:26,560
 ni biskupa,

1149
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:27,560
 nema tako jako frajera,

1150
00:41:27,560 --> 00:41:29,560
 koji mu ne treba netko,

1151
00:41:29,560 --> 00:41:31,560
 ko će ga štititi,

1152
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:33,560
 i ko me će reći,

1153
00:41:33,560 --> 00:41:35,560
 koga budete nekoga,

1154
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:37,560
 kao tko je taj jak?

1155
00:41:37,560 --> 00:41:40,560
 Tko je taj jak?

1156
00:41:40,560 --> 00:41:42,560
 Tko je taj kojačio čovjek?

1157
00:41:42,560 --> 00:41:45,560
 Dakle, to je knijedog svijeta,

1158
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:48,560
 koji je prevario Adama i Ježi.

1159
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:49,560
 Prevario ih ih,

1160
00:41:49,560 --> 00:41:50,560
 ako su bili,

1161
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:52,560
 u posebnoj minosti,

1162
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:54,560
 kad je grijeh nije bio ranio,

1163
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:55,560
 kad je grijeh nije bio,

1164
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:57,560
 učinio ono moćali njihov,

1165
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:58,560
 i mudrost,

1166
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,560
 i voju,

1167
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:00,560
 i slobodu.

1168
00:42:00,560 --> 00:42:03,560
 A kad ih je grijeh ranio,

1169
00:42:03,560 --> 00:42:05,560
 oni su,

1170
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:05,560
 dakle,

1171
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:06,560
 saki grijeh,

